Installation Instructions
*************************

What you need installed
***********************

cmake-2.4 (this is the build system used)
gtk+-2
libglade-2
gmodule-2
gtkglext-1.0
OpenCascade6.1


Compile and run instructions
****************************

1. set CASROOT environment variable
2. run cmake
3. run make
4. execute ark3d


Here's an example of the build and run process on my machine
**********************************************

export CASROOT=~/opencascade-6.1/ros
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/OpenCASCADE-6.1/lib
export LDFLAGS=-L/opt/OpenCASCADE-6.1/lib
cmake .
make
./src/ark3d



